name: Rebelle [2009]
description:
"Rebelle" features ten songs, including a new version of fan-favorite "How to Believe" (featured on Delta Airlines' "Indie Spotlight Playlist"), OurStage's #1 Pop Winner "It's Your Love", and "After You", voted #1 by fans for MTV's VMA Best Breakout Award (NYC). 

1. Praying for Rain
2. It's Your Love
3. Hollywood to Me
4. How to Believe
5. Once Again
6. Between the Lies
7. Fall
8. After You
9. Midnight Lullaby
10. Glass
